cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.ET, cs.SE, cs.AI

The paper deals with the optimization of energy storage for performing energy arbitrage and power factor correction. This involves control and optimization of power systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of energy storage for power factor correction is a common technique in power systems, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also deals with the optimization of energy storage, which falls under the category of energy (cs.ET). The use of optimization techniques for energy storage control falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
